metadata.description: Motion instruction to gait dictionary. Maps 12 semantic motion concepts to neural network weight vectors for a 3-link PyBullet robot. Each entry includes the best exemplar weight vector, all matched variants, and behavioral metrics.
metadata.robot: 3-link body (Torso + BackLeg + FrontLeg), 2 hinge joints, 3 touch sensors, 2 motors
metadata.weight_keys: w03=Torso->BackMotor, w04=Torso->FrontMotor, w13=BackLeg->BackMotor, w14=BackLeg->FrontMotor, w23=FrontLeg->BackMotor, w24=FrontLeg->FrontMotor
metadata.simulation: 4000 steps @ 240 Hz, MAX_FORCE=150N, headless PyBullet DIRECT mode

stumble.description: Irregular, unsteady motion with high variability

limp.description: Asymmetric gait with unequal leg phases

glide.description: Efficient locomotion with smooth speed profile

bounce.description: Oscillatory motion with high energy but low displacement
